com.im.njams.sdk.argos

Class ArgosMultiCollector<T extends ArgosMetric>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.argos.ArgosMultiCollector<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the metric that this collector creates.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArgosCollector

    public abstract class ArgosMultiCollector<T extends ArgosMetric>
extends Object
    Abstract base class for an ArgosCollector that collects several metrics of the same type.

    Extend this class, implement the collect method and register it in ArgosSender
